&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Return &lt;em&gt;the maximum area of a piece of cake after you cut at each horizontal and vertical position provided in the arrays&lt;/em&gt; &lt;code&gt;horizontalCuts&lt;/code&gt; &lt;em&gt;and&lt;/em&gt; &lt;code&gt;verticalCuts&lt;/code&gt;. Since the answer can be a large number, return this &lt;strong&gt;modulo&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;109 + 7&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
