    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;Problem&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Problem&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Problem&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Problem&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Evaluate the value of an arithmetic expression in &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reverse_Polish_notation&quot;&gt;Reverse Polish Notation&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Valid operators are &lt;code&gt;+&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;-&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;*&lt;/code&gt;, and &lt;code&gt;/&lt;/code&gt;. Each operand may be an integer or another expression.&lt;/p&gt;
